{"about_the_game":"Mow-down at the hoedown!  <br><br>Pack your bags and move to the idyllic countryside. Pay no heed to the nuclear fallout \u2013 it adds a lovely glow to your complexion! Upsides \u2013 everyone wants a piece of you! Downsides \u2013 everyone wants a piece of you... <br> <br>Grab your blunderbuss and get ready for twin-stick, bullet-hell, roguelite, corn-chuckin' action game that will last until the cows come home! As any self-respecting farmer would: Farm. Marry. Kill. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/757320/extras/Atomicrops_FARM.gif?t=1729070174\" /><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Sow and harvest as many fast-growing crops as you can before the day is done to earn a huge profit. Purchase weapons and items in town at the end of each day. Celebrate the end of each season with special shops and rewards. <br></li><li>Permanently Upgrade your farming and fighting abilities. Earn a payout each run that can be used on permanent improvements and unlocks. <br></li><li>Progress through the years with ramping difficulty and even greater rewards! </li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/757320/extras/Atomicrops_MARRY.gif?t=1729070174\" /><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Befriend an entourage of pig pals, chicken chums, and cow colleagues to automate farming tasks. Woo and marry a kindred spirit from the local town to fight and farm alongside you. <br></li><li>Unlock new characters, spouses, difficulties, and permanent upgrades. Most importantly, you can unlock many cats to permanently roam your homestead (yes, you can pet them).</li></ul> <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/757320/extras/Atomicrops_KILL.gif?t=1729070174\" /><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Defend your crops from unforgiving nightly attackers looking to rampage your hard-earned harvest. <br></li><li>Fight challenging bosses each season until you reach the final season - the Nuclear Winter.  <br></li><li>Explore the far reaches of the biomes to find useful relics of farms long past. Powerful loot increases your farming abilities and helps you fight enemies. </li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Cashew Out","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/757320/286855a9dccb93bc11678b8f904bc90d66351a32.jpg"},{"name":"Cashew on the Flipside","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/757320/ef9924a5a3885e7334071cc843ac88f378478ba4.jpg"},{"name":"Cashew Is King","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/757320/e81d7f95474a5c4ba5afbbe1fcd26f454c22bf5c.jpg"},{"name":"Timber","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/757320/63398bbafd878b25e96b3e577ce4a7967bb34793.jpg"},{"name":"Arboreal Deal","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/757320/c4a44f4c9100a118532c5860daa37c1143834af7.jpg"},{"name":"Extra Fries","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/757320/1de15076b6bf74d387ca78824d2074742f6ea41f.jpg"},{"name":"Beeson D'etre","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/757320/9ed3827894e440a8c0f91b907ab38aff701205f4.jpg"},{"name":"New Year Lotus","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/757320/ca4593c05633f54179e579c1e749262d3008c11b.jpg"},{"name":"Demi-Decade Orchid","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/757320/d2e0a6d6d11c307805ec95d4f10df6dbabe6005b.jpg"},{"name":"Corpse Flower","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/757320/dbacb8aaf0f40f7ed24ca34efcdfe607ee49861a.jpg"}],"total":26},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/757320/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=17290701